{
  "stem": "15396.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "A lot of-- gangsters were helpful, let's put it that way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And a lot of people with ties and all with gangsters, too, I have to tell you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then a lot of wonderful people who did wonderful things, did dangerous things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And this-- Harry Bingham, you know, the vice-consul.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He could have ruined his career and a lot of other things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Career is nothing, but what could have happened to him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There were some wonderful people in that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think those moments bring out the best and the worst in people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Fry was the kind of man who you either laughed at him or you really loved him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think sometimes these people say, oh, what could he do?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, he did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had to make a speech, a big thing, with the opening of the museum at the-- at the Department of Commerce.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Big, bit thing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Another one in the rotunda at the Capitol.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said that it should have been mission accomplished rather than surrender on demand, because surrender on demand is a little bit negative for what he did.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's his book, the name of his book.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You must get that book.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And get Mary Jane's book.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's good.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Danny Benedict wrote one in French, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A lot of people wrote about this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] No.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not yet, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As I say, you know, there's not-- it's in the back of your mind, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A lot of things have happened, and as I say, most of my friends-- a girl I knew quite well in Rome rushed up to me one day, and she'd read something in one of the American magazines about me, and said, I didn't know you'd ever done anything.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were the ones who were doing it.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
